<p>[2] Christov-Moore, et al. (2014). Empathy: gender effects in brain and behavior. Neuroscience &amp; Biobehavioral Reviews, 46, 604-627. </p>
<p>[3] Kirkland, et al. (2013). Meta-analysis R eveals Adult Female Superiority in" Reading the Mind in the Eyes Test". North American Journal of Psychology, 15(1). </p>
<p>[4] De Waal, FB (2008). Putting the altruism back into altruism: the evolution of empathy. Annu. Rev. Psychol. , 59 , 279-300. </p>
